<tr><td>and falls of the flank for respiration rate.</td></tr>
<tr><td>3. Normal respiration of a cattle is about 25 to 50 breaths per</td></tr>
<tr><td>minute, and that of a goats is about 12 to 25 breaths per</td></tr>
<tr><td>minute.</td></tr>
